        ". It was probably in this period that he wrote his first novel, Ofiara ; he is thought to have destroyed the manuscript of the never-published novel. He also worked on his first novel to be published, Na marne . He completed extramural secondary-school classes, and in 1866 he received his secondary-school diploma. He first tried to study medicine, then law, at the ": null
