    },
    {
        ". He completed his university studies in 1871, though he failed to receive a diploma because he did not pass the examination in ": null
    },
    {
        "Greek language": "Greek Language"
    },
    {
        ". Sienkiewicz also wrote for Gazeta Polska and Niwa , under the pen name Litwos . In 1873 he began writing a column,  Bez tytułu , in The Polish Gazette; in 1874 a column, Sprawy bieżące for Niwa; and in 1875 the column, Chwila obecna . He also collaborated on a Polish translation, published in 1874, of ": null
    },
    {
