        ". His travels were financed by Gazeta Polska in exchange for a series of travel essays: Sienkiewicz wrote Listy z podróży and Listy Litwosa z Podróży , which were published in The Polish Gazette in 1876–78 and republished as a book in 1880. Other articles by him also appeared in Przegląd Tygodniowy and Przewodnik Naukowy i Literacki , discussing the situation of ": null
