        ". He supported educational endeavors and co-founded the Polska Macierz Szkolna organization. Reasonably wealthy by 1908 thanks to sales of his books, he often used his new wealth to support struggling writers. He helped gather funds for social-welfare projects such as starvation relief, and for construction of a tuberculosis sanatorium at ": null
