    },
    {
        "naturalistic": "Naturalism"
    },
    {
        " philosophies. He had expressed his opinions on naturalism and writing, generally, early on in O naturaliźmie w powieści . A dozen years later, in 1893, he wrote that novels should strengthen and ennoble life, rather than undermining and debasing it. Later, in the early 1900s, he fell into mutual hostility with the ": null
    },
    {
